						               													<description>Players begin the game with 5 cards and they choose which number on each card they will use to bluff and win the round. During a round, each player must either make a bid of how many of a certain die they believe are shared amongst all players chosen dice -OR- call the previous player's bluff and say, &amp;quot;LIE!&amp;quot; The loser of the round may only draw back up to 4 cards next round and play continues until just one player remains!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are several unique aspects to this 30-card mini micro game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Players choose which dice they will bid and bluff with each round.&amp;#10;2. Each player holds extra hidden information based on which dice they DIDN'T use for the round.&amp;#10;3. The first player to bid in a round must choose which direction the bidding will proceed in.&amp;#10;4. 2 to 6 Players can play!&amp;#10;5. Several variants included.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Number 6 in the Pack O Game series.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
